  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "As a solution, we pre-detected them in the preprocessing stage.",
    "We applied the latest approach for text reuse detection in ancient Chinese (Duan et al., 2023), which uses pretrained deep learning models (Vaswani et al., 2017; Devlin et al., 2019; Liu et al., 2019) and contrastive learning (Gao et al., 2021) to get personalized text similarity models without supervision, thereby detecting text reuses within ancient Chinese literature through sentence embedding similarity.",
    "Currently, we have identified over 14 million text reuses in this corpus, and this number is continuously increasing.",
    "We saved the results as index IDs in the JSON file, corresponding to the document data.",
    "The system accesses this data in text reuse browsing and analysis."
  ],
